{"tid":1005286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一年前廣州小朋友唔講粵話，一年後香港步後塵","createTime":"2019-02-02T05:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T05:55:26.000Z","uid":234763,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed10ee9b4702854fd988513dd219d8bd9ed2b4a","tid":1005286,"uid":234763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"原來之前有線中國組做過廣州小朋友唔講粵語嘅報導，嗰時仲係講廣州有三成青年人唔識粵語。<br />\n一年之後，發現香港啲細路已經唔講廣東話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要嗰間咩嘢「香港普通話研習社 科技創意小學」明目張膽用「Xianggang」唔用「Hong Kong」做英文名。真係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年前廣州：<br />\n【粵語傳承有困難】 【三成廣州青少年不會廣東話】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1589603941184086/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1589603941184086%2F&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2R4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=f05bf70f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1589603941184086/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日香港：<br />\n【普通話成為小學生的日常用語？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/1120586354811676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnews.lancet%2Fvideos%2F1120586354811676&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2R4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=7295cc7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/1120586354811676</a><br />\n<br />\n題外話：<br />\n其實普教中，滅粵語應該部署咗十幾廿年。因為細個嗰時老師成日話普通話學中文好啲，可以做到「我手寫我口」，嗰時啲家長仲會爭住送啲仔女入「試行」普教中中學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}